reviewtext: As I have mentioned in other reviews of Fuji film products, this one is no exception.  The ISO 200 is an excellent medium for generating some fine color prints.  I highly recommend this company and the film offerings they have.Their pricing is more than fair and processing does not take very long.  If you like film photography as I do, and have not tried Fuji products, I highly recommend firing off a test roll.  Thanks for reading.Tony
summary: Able to leap tall buildings at a single bound, more powerful than a locomotive and faster than a speeding bullet.
